{
  "stem": "2133.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we were put in that train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, it was the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now it was snowing, and it was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] really, we had no food, nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when somebody died, we just took their clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were happy to get their clothes and get a little warm, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by the time I arrived to Buchenwald, I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I must have been completely out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wouldn't say in a coma, but I was unconscious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was put together with the dead people from the train who died in this journey.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was told, which I didn't know, that one of the people who worked in the crematorium, one of the other prisoner that took me down, he seen that I still had some life in me and took me out of the dead people.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I just ended up in one of the barracks, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's the way I woke up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't know where I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That must have been the spring of 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometime in February, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Or March.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they used to call it the infirmatary there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed there, you know, in those bunk, on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- In a hospital, you mean?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hospital, infirmatary, they called--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Infirmary.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we stayed there for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told that I had seen terrible things through those years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I never experienced anything like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As we were looking out from our bunk, there was another transport come in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these people came completely naked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were undressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't look people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were beaten in each other's flesh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Was gobs of flesh was all over on the body.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
